What does Coach Patrick do on vacation? Runs to the nearest running store and makes new friends! Thanks to Darrell and Mark (hat) for the hospitality and chat about Utah running. Darrell gave a tip about a path I never would have found on my own. @wasatchrunning #runnersofinstagram #runningfriends #lessoxygenuphere

Celebrate Global Running Day with Fleet Feet Sports! The Big Run 5k is a run/walk on June 6th and is being held in conjunction with the Santa Rosa Wednesday Night Market. The theme is Super Heroes so start planning your outfit now! Register today on fleetfeetsantarosa.com and make sure to stop by the store to check out the Fleet Feet exclusive colors of the Adrenaline that Brooks has released in honor of the run!
